{Nightshade}

    "5....4....3....2...late...." She spoke a second before both det charges
exploded with the force of a small tank of nitro, engulfing the cellblock,
the coorridor beyond and several ajoining rooms in all consuming flame and
twisted metal as the shockwave literally tore apart the metallic walls which
surrounded them, her last words, "See you in what the humans use to call
Hell Sunhawk..."
